    "Significantly, DE3TC improves by 1.98% in F1 score of Tri-CLS over the best performance baselines, CorED-BERT.",
    "On the CASIE dataset, our method significantly outperforms baseline methods, achieving a 10.78% improvement in F1 score compared to Text2Event.",
    "(2) Compared with DEGREE on ACE 2005, the event extraction method using prompts with manually designed type descriptions and keywords, our model outperforms it significantly.",
